    <div class="container">
      <span style="font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--color-text-faint); letter-spacing: 0.05em; text-transform: uppercase;">In the media</span>
      <h2>Press &amp; media coverage</h2>
      <p>My research on institutional design, polarisation, and democracy has been covered in Belgian and international media.</p>
      <div class="pub-list">
        <div class="pub-item">
          <div>
            <p class="pub-title">Polarisatie: bedreiging of motor voor democratie? — press release PhD</p>
